Title: Email Address Field in contact us section accepts invalid email address.

Description: When i enter any invalid email address for example abc@abc.com, input field accepts it.

Steps to reproduce: Go to "Contact Us" in the navigation bar, 
type in a value in the "email address" input field.

Environment: Google Chrome

Expected results: Invalid email address.

Assigned to: Rajoy Chowdhury

Severity: Medium.